## Risk Escalation Tiers (separate from regime)

These operate independently of L1 and L2 — a kill switch fires regardless of regime:

| Tier | Trigger | Action |
|---|---|---|
| **Tier 1 — Kill Switch** | Manual or auto-triggered at -8% drawdown | All trading halted immediately |
| **Tier 2 — Drawdown Breaker** | -3% → size 50%; -5% → halt entries | Graduated position size reduction |
| **Tier 3 — Assignment Monitor** | Options approaching/inside ITM | Telegram alerts, no automatic halt |

See `risk-monitoring.mdc` for executor check patterns.

